commitResults.messageBody:
Added the ability to read and write student list into course data file.
Students were stored in course data using student id strings.
For read data, an observableList of Person was passed in to match
the student id from data file.

improved the abstraction of course methods on student list
 following OOP principal.

Fixed the deregister command to make sure all student has been removed
 from courses before deleting it.
improved test for RemoveStudentCommand to improve test coverage
update UiClassDiagram to include course ui

The Person class treats two person with same name
 to be the same person

 We now treat two person with same student id to be the same person.
 This is to better suit to EB requirements

student id now will increment according to the latest student id

remove dependency of getLatestStudentId on userPref
